Name: Ancient Knowledge
About the game: Ancient knowledge is a story in which you will explore the ruins of settlements of the powerful ancient civilization that lived here long time ago, overcoming the traps and puzzles they left. Main features: - Nice low poly graphics and attention to detail - Magical atmosphere that will allow you to immerse yourself in the culture of ancient India - Explore ancient palaces and temples, overcoming many traps - A large number of different types of puzzles
